address.streetAddress: Southport Plan, Colony at Lexington Plantation

location.fullValue: Southport Plan, Colony at Lexington Plantation

data.description: Don't let this stunning home in the sought-after Lexington Plantation neighborhood slip through your fingers! With upgraded hardwood flooring on the first floor. The family-friendly living room boasts an open concept design and a cozy gas fireplace. The spacious dining and kitchen combo is perfect for hosting family gatherings, featuring granite counters, white subway tile backsplash, upgraded lighting, stainless steel appliances, a large pantry, and beautiful, rich cabinets. Upstairs, a wide hallway leads to the laundry room, 2 bedrooms, a bathroom, and a breathtaking master suite complete with a separate shower, garden tub, & 2 closets. Venture to the 3rd floor to discover the expansive 4th bedroom/bonus space & includes a full bathroom, closet, and wet bar-perfect for: in-law suite, guest room, or home theater... the possibilities are endless! Enjoy community amenities such as a pool, gym, and playground. All this without the burden of city taxes!
